This paper is likely to belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category as it deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis. Additionally, the use of lexical and semantic features suggests the involvement of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also involves social media analysis, which could fall under the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-category. Finally, the use of weighted F1-measures suggests the involvement of statistical analysis and probability theory, which could fall under the Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-category.
